---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="SMS Terms of Service | StemCyte">

<style is:global>
  .pp-header { background:#3D0F31; padding:140px 48px 56px; }
  .pp-header-inner { max-width:800px; margin:0 auto; }
  .pp-header .lbl { font-size:11px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:1.5px; text-transform:uppercase; color:#E8A0D0; margin-bottom:12px; }
  .pp-header h1 { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:40px; font-weight:400; line-height:1.15; letter-spacing:-1px; color:#fff; margin-bottom:12px; }
  .pp-header .sub { font-size:15px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); line-height:1.7; }

  .pp-body { max-width:800px; margin:0 auto; padding:56px 48px 80px; }
  .pp-intro { font-size:16px; line-height:1.8; color:#5A564E; margin-bottom:16px; }

  .pp-section { margin-top:40px; }
  .pp-section-num { font-size:11px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:1.5px; text-transform:uppercase; color:#6C1A55; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .pp-section h2 { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:24px; font-weight:400; letter-spacing:-0.3px; color:#2C2A26; margin-bottom:16px; line-height:1.3; }
  .pp-section h3 { font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:#2C2A26; margin-bottom:8px; margin-top:20px; }
  .pp-section h3:first-of-type { margin-top:0; }
  .pp-section p { font-size:15px; line-height:1.8; color:#5A564E; margin-bottom:12px; }
  .pp-section ul { margin:12px 0 12px 24px; }
  .pp-section ul li { font-size:15px; line-height:1.8; color:#5A564E; margin-bottom:6px; padding-left:4px; }
  .pp-section ul li::marker { color:#C9A0C0; }
  .pp-section a { color:#6C1A55; text-decoration:underline; text-underline-offset:2px; }
  .pp-section a:hover { color:#8B2E72; }

  .pp-contact-block { background:#F3F0F8; border-radius:12px; padding:24px 28px; margin-top:12px; }
  .pp-contact-block p { font-size:15px; line-height:1.8; color:#5A564E; margin-bottom:4px; }
  .pp-contact-block p:last-child { margin-bottom:0; }
  .pp-contact-block a { color:#6C1A55; text-decoration:underline; text-underline-offset:2px; }

  @media (max-width:900px) {
    .pp-header { padding:120px 24px 40px; }
    .pp-header h1 { font-size:32px; }
    .pp-body { padding:40px 24px 64px; }
  }
  @media (max-width:600px) {
    .pp-header { padding:100px 20px 32px; }
    .pp-header h1 { font-size:28px; }
    .pp-body { padding:32px 20px 48px; }
    .pp-section h2 { font-size:20px; }
  }
</style>

<div class="pp-header" id="hero">
  <div class="pp-header-inner">
    <div class="lbl">Legal</div>
    <h1>SMS Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="sub">Terms governing text message communications from StemCyte.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="pp-body">
  <p class="pp-intro">By opting in to receive SMS messages from StemCyte, Inc. (&ldquo;StemCyte&rdquo;), you agree to receive text messages at the mobile number you provide. These SMS Terms of Service govern your receipt of text messages from StemCyte.</p>

  <div class="pp-section">
    <div class="pp-section-num">Types of Messages</div>
    <h2>Types of Messages</h2>
    <p>Messages from StemCyte may include the following categories:</p>

    <h3>Service and Operational Messages</h3>
    <p>Non-marketing communications necessary to support your relationship with StemCyte, such as:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Kit shipment or tracking notifications</li>
      <li>Account or enrollment notices</li>
      <li>Required consent, documentation, or compliance reminders</li>
      <li>Service updates related to collection, processing, or storage</li>
      <li>Customer support responses or follow-ups</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Transactional Messages</h3>
    <p>Messages confirming actions you have taken, including enrollment confirmations, payment-related notices, or status updates tied to a specific request.</p>

    <h3>Event and Webinar Messages</h3>
    <p>Reminders and updates related to webinars, events, or educational sessions you have registered for.</p>

    <h3>Marketing and Promotional Messages (Optional)</h3>
    <p>Messages related to promotions, educational offerings, or other marketing communications, where permitted by law and based on your consent preferences.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pp-section">
    <div class="pp-section-num">Frequency</div>
    <h2>Message Frequency</h2>
    <p>Message frequency varies by message type. You may receive multiple messages related to a specific event or transaction, and occasional messages for marketing purposes if you have opted in.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pp-section">
    <div class="pp-section-num">Rates</div>
    <h2>Message and Data Rates</h2>
    <p>Message and data rates may apply. Please contact your wireless carrier for details about your messaging plan.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pp-section">
    <div class="pp-section-num">Opt-Out</div>
    <h2>Opt-Out</h2>
    <p>You may opt out of all SMS messages at any time by replying STOP to any message you receive from StemCyte. After opting out, you will receive a confirmation message and will no longer receive SMS messages from us unless you opt in again.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pp-section">
    <div class="pp-section-num">Help</div>
    <h2>Help</h2>
    <p>For help or questions about SMS messaging from StemCyte, reply HELP to any message, or contact us at <a href="mailto:customerservice@stemcyte.com">customerservice@stemcyte.com</a>.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pp-section">
    <div class="pp-section-num">Data Sharing</div>
    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>StemCyte does not use SMS messaging to request or transmit confidential medical, genetic, or highly sensitive health information.</p>
    <p>Mobile opt-in data and consent will not be shared with any third parties for their marketing purposes. SMS-related information is used solely to deliver messages, manage communication preferences, and comply with applicable legal and regulatory requirements.</p>
    <p>All the above categories exclude text messaging originator opt-in data and consent. This information will not be shared with any third parties, excluding aggregators and providers of text message services.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pp-section">
    <div class="pp-section-num">Carrier Disclaimer</div>
    <h2>Carrier Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>Carriers are not liable for delayed or undelivered messages. Delivery of messages is subject to effective transmission from your wireless carrier and network availability.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pp-section">
    <div class="pp-section-num">Privacy</div>
    <h2>Privacy</h2>
    <p>For information on how StemCyte collects, uses, and protects your personal information, please see our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pp-section">
    <div class="pp-section-num">Contact</div>
    <h2>Contact Information</h2>
    <div class="pp-contact-block">
      <p><strong>StemCyte International, Ltd.</strong></p>
      <p>13800 Live Oak Ave</p>
      <p>Baldwin Park, CA 91706</p>
      <p>Email: <a href="mailto:customerservice@stemcyte.com">customerservice@stemcyte.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

</BaseLayout>
